Title: AN ACT CHANGING THE NAME OF THE BARRIO OF LONGOS, PILILLA, RIZAL, TO THAT OF MALAYA.
Data:
[ Commonwealth Act No. 574, June 08, 1940 ]
AN ACT CHANGING THE NAME OF THE BARRIO OF LONGOS, PILILLA, RIZAL, TO THAT OF MALAYA.
Be it enacted by the National Assembly of the Philippines:
Section 1. The name of the barrio of Longos, municipality of Pililla, Province of Rizal, is changed to that of Malaya.ℒαwρhi৷
Section 2. This Act shall take effect on its approval.
Enacted, without Executive approval, June 8, 1940.
